00:36:56,280 --> 00:36:57,120
At that time,...

579
00:36:58,120 --> 00:37:00,000
both Xiaomeng and I
were with a sports school.

580
00:37:00,280 --> 00:37:01,440
I was with the boxing team

581
00:37:01,760 --> 00:37:02,960
while she was
with the artistic gymnastics team.

582
00:37:04,360 --> 00:37:05,400
Come to think of it,...

583
00:37:06,960 --> 00:37:08,440
we were so carefree.

584
00:37:10,760 --> 00:37:12,240
How I wish you could be less busy.

585
00:37:13,320 --> 00:37:15,480
Then you can tell me
more about your young...

586
00:37:16,680 --> 00:37:18,200
you and Xiaomeng's

587
00:37:18,320 --> 00:37:20,080
younger days.

588
00:37:22,800 --> 00:37:24,000
But who would expect...

589
00:37:25,040 --> 00:37:26,200
the boxer to become...

590
00:37:27,400 --> 00:37:29,880
the boss of a real estate company now.

591
00:37:30,600 --> 00:37:32,720
All he faces every day
are graphs and reports,...

592
00:37:33,720 --> 00:37:35,000
and invisible opponents

593
00:37:35,360 --> 00:37:37,240
who constantly threaten him.

594
00:37:38,480 --> 00:37:41,240
A Yan, although I don't know

595
00:37:41,680 --> 00:37:42,960
much about the business sector,

596
00:37:43,360 --> 00:37:44,320
I believe

597
00:37:44,520 --> 00:37:45,600
you can do it.

598
00:37:45,760 --> 00:37:46,760
You'll succeed.

599
00:37:47,360 --> 00:37:48,680
I fully support you.

600
00:37:50,800 --> 00:37:51,600
Aunt Lin,...

601
00:37:52,320 --> 00:37:54,000
I wonder what's wrong with me today.

602
00:37:54,440 --> 00:37:56,320
When I saw you, I felt close to you

603
00:37:56,720 --> 00:37:58,320
and wanted to tell you more.

604
00:37:59,400 --> 00:38:01,360
Me too. Seeing you

605
00:38:01,480 --> 00:38:02,920
reminds me of my family.

606
00:38:06,480 --> 00:38:07,880
Excuse me, Aunt Lin.
I've to take this call.

607
00:38:08,000 --> 00:38:08,920
Okay.

608
00:38:12,160 --> 00:38:12,960
Hello.

609
00:38:23,200 --> 00:38:24,520
Okay, I get it.

610
00:38:25,320 --> 00:38:26,560
I'll go back to the office now.

611
00:38:33,680 --> 00:38:34,520
Aunt Lin, you...

612
00:38:34,560 --> 00:38:37,000
Lately, my eyes tend to become watery

613
00:38:37,040 --> 00:38:38,840
whenever wind blows into my eyes.

614
00:38:41,000 --> 00:38:42,720
Something urgent crops up in the office.

615
00:38:42,760 --> 00:38:43,840
I've to go back.

616
00:38:44,320 --> 00:38:46,520
Work is more important.

617
00:38:47,400 --> 00:38:49,040
Take care and drive carefully.

618
00:38:50,040 --> 00:38:51,320
Okay. I'll see you again.

619
00:39:31,360 --> 00:39:33,480
Tiankong, tell me

620
00:39:33,520 --> 00:39:34,520
if you need anything.

621
00:39:34,640 --> 00:39:36,640
You must not touch your eyes
with your hands.

622
00:39:46,040 --> 00:39:48,360
It's a little bear.

623
00:39:49,680 --> 00:39:51,160
Tiankong, you're so smart.

624
00:39:51,400 --> 00:39:52,600
You know everything.

625
00:39:53,400 --> 00:39:54,440
Sister Xiaomeng,

626
00:39:54,560 --> 00:39:56,240
I had a dream just now.

627
00:39:56,400 --> 00:39:58,240
It's a colorful dream.

628
00:39:58,280 --> 00:39:59,520
There was a forest.

629
00:39:59,840 --> 00:40:02,400
There were lots of beautiful flowers,

630
00:40:02,560 --> 00:40:05,200
many animals and...

631
00:40:05,760 --> 00:40:06,600
What else?

632
00:40:06,640 --> 00:40:08,080
Father and Mother.

633
00:40:10,160 --> 00:40:11,520
Father and Mother?

634
00:40:11,800 --> 00:40:14,480
Yes, I saw Father and Mother just now.

635
00:40:16,560 --> 00:40:19,160
Have you met them before?

636
00:40:20,600 --> 00:40:23,440
Mom Lin said I'm an abandoned baby.

637
00:40:23,600 --> 00:40:25,360
Someone picked me up on a roadside

638
00:40:25,400 --> 00:40:27,320
and brought me to the welfare center.

639
00:40:27,600 --> 00:40:29,000
Sister Xiaomeng,

640
00:40:29,040 --> 00:40:30,640
they didn't want me.

641
00:40:30,680 --> 00:40:32,400
Is it because I was not good enough

642
00:40:32,440 --> 00:40:34,520
so they didn't like me?

643
00:40:38,800 --> 00:40:39,640
Tiankong,

644
00:40:40,000 --> 00:40:41,640
it's not true that they don't like you.

645
00:40:42,000 --> 00:40:43,160
They're just...

646
00:40:45,680 --> 00:40:47,600
afraid they can't take good care of you.

647
00:40:48,400 --> 00:40:50,480
Mom Lin told me that too.

648
00:40:50,800 --> 00:40:53,040
But I'm their child.

649
00:40:53,160 --> 00:40:54,920
I don't need them to take care of me.

650
00:40:55,120 --> 00:40:57,600
I can take care of myself.

651
00:40:58,040 --> 00:40:59,840
I just miss them

652
00:41:00,200 --> 00:41:02,400
and want to live with them.

653
00:41:02,800 --> 00:41:04,840
Even in my dream, I don't know

654
00:41:04,960 --> 00:41:06,160
how they look like.

655
00:41:06,320 --> 00:41:07,560
But I'm very sure

656
00:41:07,680 --> 00:41:09,440
they're my father and mother.

657
00:41:09,600 --> 00:41:12,320
They waved and smiled to me.

658
00:41:15,520 --> 00:41:17,120
Tiankong,

659
00:41:17,160 --> 00:41:19,960
if you find your parents one day,...

660
00:41:20,680 --> 00:41:21,800
will you blame them?

661
00:41:22,440 --> 00:41:24,600
No, I'll forgive them.

662
00:41:24,800 --> 00:41:27,080
Then they'll love me more

663
00:41:27,120 --> 00:41:28,800
and stay by my side.

664
00:41:32,200 --> 00:41:34,480
Tiankong, do you know this?

665
00:41:34,840 --> 00:41:36,360
You're the most understanding child

666
00:41:36,400 --> 00:41:38,520
I've ever met.

667
00:41:39,360 --> 00:41:40,520
Right?

668
00:41:49,040 --> 00:41:49,880
Director Lin.

669
00:41:53,840 --> 00:41:54,760
Director Lin!

670
00:41:57,840 --> 00:41:58,920
What's wrong?

671
00:41:58,960 --> 00:42:00,240
Nothing.

672
00:42:00,280 --> 00:42:03,120
Is it because of A Yan?

673
00:42:03,680 --> 00:42:04,680
No.

674
00:42:05,840 --> 00:42:07,320
We had a good talk.

675
00:42:08,840 --> 00:42:09,720
That's good.

676
00:42:10,480 --> 00:42:11,840
I was worried.

677
00:42:13,840 --> 00:42:14,680
Director Lin,

678
00:42:15,040 --> 00:42:17,320
is there anything wrong

679
00:42:17,360 --> 00:42:18,600
with A Yan?

680
00:42:20,480 --> 00:42:21,680
He doesn't know anything.

681
00:42:22,920 --> 00:42:23,880
It's me.

682
00:42:25,880 --> 00:42:28,480
Xiaomeng, the problem

683
00:42:28,520 --> 00:42:29,480
lies with me.

684
00:42:29,920 --> 00:42:31,120
I'm afraid I can't hold it in.

685
00:42:31,720 --> 00:42:32,560
You've no idea.

686
00:42:33,400 --> 00:42:36,280
Whenever I see his eyes, I...

687
00:42:36,920 --> 00:42:37,880
They look almost the same

688
00:42:37,920 --> 00:42:39,640
as mine when I was young.

689
00:42:40,000 --> 00:42:42,200
Whenever I see him, I want to tell him...

690
00:42:43,480 --> 00:42:45,560
that I'm his mother.

691
00:42:45,680 --> 00:42:47,320
I'm his mother.

692
00:42:47,480 --> 00:42:48,600
Calm down.

693
00:42:48,720 --> 00:42:50,240
Now isn't the time yet.
